snippet.title: Pathway to Glory  Ikusa Islands Trailer
snippet.description: This time, you lead your soldiers on the pacific war theatre. On sun drenched islands, through the humid stench of the jungle and into the narrow back streets of the cities, you fight side by side, pushing back the enemy inch by inch. An enemy that would much rather face certain death than the disgrace of surrender. Although your troops are seasoned veterans who have learned the horrible mechanics of war while liberating Europe, nothing could have prepared them for this.
